| Plot                    = The [[Guardians of the Galaxy (Earth-TRN971)|Guardians of the Galaxy]] have been captured by [[Taneleer Tivan (Earth-TRN971)|The Collector]] to become the newest prized attraction in the [[Collector's Museum|The Collector’s Fortress]]. However, [[89P13 (Earth-TRN971)|Rocket]] was able to escape. With the help of [[Earth-1218#Residents|numerous unnamed Terrans]], Rocket was able to hack into the Collector's system, take over the gantry lifts, free the other Guardians, and play music from Star-Lord's [[Awesome Mix]].

After being freed, the Guardians were picked up by [[Mantis (Earth-TRN971)|Mantis]] in the [[Milano]].

